## Typography

### Primary — F37 Bobby Regular
- Usage: All headlines and subheadings H1–H4
- Letter spacing (tracking): **−60 (−3%)**
- Style: Serif display typeface

### Secondary — F37 Jan Family
- Usage: Body copy, sub-headings H5 and below, UI text
- Weights available: **Regular** and **Bold**
- Style: Sans-serif, versatile

### Hierarchy
| Level | Font | Weight | Usage |
|---|---|---|---|
| H1–H4 | F37 Bobby | Regular | Display, headlines |
| H5+ | F37 Jan | Bold | Sub-headings |
| Body | F37 Jan | Regular | Paragraphs, UI copy |
| CTA / Label | F37 Jan | Bold | Buttons, labels |

