## Brand Voice

### Tone Scales
| Dimension | Position |
|---|---|
| Energy | Upbeat (3/5) |
| Intimacy | Partner (4/5) |
| Attitude | Polite opinionated (2/5) |
| Intelligence | Smart (3/5) |
| Humour | Intelligent wit (3/5) |

### Voice Principles

**Be personable**
Adopt a friendly, conversational tone. Communicate as if speaking to a close colleague.

**Be impactful**
Deliver real value with everything we say. Include relevant, insightful, and clear explanations.

**Be clear**
Use direct and everyday language. No embellishments or unnecessary jargon.

**Be inclusive**
Use respectful, people-first language. Focus on the person — not their disability or condition.

